titles.title: A concurrent resolution providing for a correction in the enrollment of S. 2553.
A concurrent resolution providing for a correction in the enrollment of S. 2553.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.
Without objection, the Chair laid before the House S.Con.Res. 49. The concurrent resolution was agreed to and the motion to reconsider was laid on the table.

bill.summary: Directs the Secretary of the Senate to make a correction in the enrollment of S. 2553 (Knowing the Lowest Price Act of 2018) to amend the title.
